
  Mightyena    Dark Type Pokémon

  MIGHTYENA gives obvious signals 
  when it is preparing to attack. 
   It starts to growl deeply and 
  then flattens its body.  This 
  Pokémon will bite savagely with 
  its sharply pointed fangs. 
	Evolution Chain
